<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((تخريج الفقه)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٧١)</span> , <span class="c2">((أحكام الجنائز)</span>) <span class="c2">(ص ١٠٧)</span> , <span class="c2">((ظلال الجنة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٧٣٥)</span>: ق.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>